extends layout

block head


block content
  style.
    section > .Icon {
      float: right;
    }

    pre { z-index: -1; }
    pre img { width: 36px; vertical-align: bottom; }

    section { clear: both; }

  p <a href="/">Back to home</a>

  h2 Emoji code

  p A tweet-size scripting language for a tweet-based game making tool.

  p.
    Each statement should be on its own line.

  section
    img.Icon(src="images/emoji/27b0.png",alt="‚û∞")
    h2 Always
    pre :curly_loop:

    p.
      Any code following the curly loop emoji will be executed every frame for each actor it is attached to.

  section
    img.Icon(src="images/emoji/1f305.png",alt="üåÖ")
    h2 Once
    pre :sunrise:
      
    p.
      Any code following the sunrise emoji will only be executed once for each actor it is attached to,
      when the actor is instantiated or when the script gets attached to it.

  section
    img.Icon(src="images/emoji/1f427.png",alt="üêß")
    h2 Current actor
    pre :penguin:

    p.
      A single script can be attached on a multitude of actors.
      The penguin emoji represents the actor the script is currently dealing with.

  section
    img.Icon(src="images/emoji/1f6a9.png",alt="üö©")
    h2 Position
    pre :triangular_flag_on_post:

    p.
      Get or set an actor's position.

    pre
      | @gdevbot 
      mark #ProjectName
      |  
      img(src="images/emoji/1f6a9.png",alt="üö©")
      mark
        img(src="images/emoji/1f427.png",alt="üêß")
      |  
      mark 20
      |  
      mark 30

  section
    img.Icon(src="images/emoji/1f697.png",alt="üöó")
    h2 Move
    pre :car:

    p.
      Move an actor by a certain offset.

    pre
      | @gdevbot 
      mark #ProjectName
      |  
      img(src="images/emoji/27b0.png",alt="‚û∞")
      img(src="images/emoji/1f697.png",alt="üöó")
      mark
        img(src="images/emoji/1f427.png",alt="üêß")
      |  
      mark 10
      |  
      mark -5

  section
    .Icon
      img(src="images/emoji/2753.png",alt="‚ùì")
    h2 Condition
    pre :question:

    p.
      Only execute the statement right after if the condition turns out to be true.

    pre
      | @gdevbot 
      mark #ProjectName
      |  
      img(src="images/emoji/2753.png",alt="‚ùì")
      mark condition
      |  
      mark statement


  section
    .Icon
      img(src="images/emoji/23e9.png",alt="‚è©")
      |  
      img(src="images/emoji/23ea.png",alt="‚è©")
    h2 Code block
    pre.
      :fast_forward:
      :rewind:

    p.
